# SegmentKey Equality operator

Tests two segment keys for equality.

```csharp

```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| left | The first segment key. |
| right | The second segment key. |

## Return Value

Returns `true` if the segment keys are equal; `false` otherwise.
